article.description: — Andre Screen scored 15 points on 7-for-10 shooting and Bucknell beat Niagara 68-50 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Screen's 15 help Bucknell knock off Niagara 68-50
article.linkText: Screen's 15 help Bucknell knock off Niagara 68-50
article.story: LEWISBURG, Pa. -- — Andre Screen scored 15 points on 7-for-10 shooting and Bucknell beat Niagara 68-50 on Saturday night. Xander Rice scored 14 points and had four steals for the Bison (2-0). Elvin Edmonds IV shot 5 for 9, including 2 for 3 from beyond the arc to finish with 12 points. Noah Thomasson scored 12 points for the Purple Eagles (0-2). NEXT UP Bucknell plays Tuesday against Saint Peter's on the road, while Niagara plays Central Arkansas on Friday. ------
